snippet.title: Line Dance Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/982370/Line_Dance_Virtual/

Line Dancing is fun! No matter where you are. Get in on the fun in Virtual Reality. Dance in a club with studio-level instruction. Choose your avatar, your dance style, and explore your dance scene. 

Private lessons, practice mode, dance mode.

Line Dance Virtual
